ygData.messageBody:
Well..I'm rather new to this (The EQ Gay thing), most folks seem so
Phobic....its terrible, but I'll likely have fun here.

First Name: Fido (Actually its Stephen, but even my mother
calls me Fido, its a dog impersonation that I can do)
Age: 30 years old - big kid
Location: Louisville, Kentucky, USA (Moved here a week ago)
(I'm a Canadian Computer Engineer, I'm just here for
the all-mighty American Dollar)
Gender: /em looks down - "male"
Home Page: N/A - Maybe when a nice person comes into my life
I'll put something on a page
Status: Single and looking
Main Character: Tkith - 51st lvl Dwarven Cleric Quellious
Biktiny - 49th lvl Gnome Enchanter Quellious
Most Hated
EQ Monster: Spite Golems - they also stop me from camping with
their really bad AoE spell - CLERICS CAMP!
Favorite
EQ Monster: The goblins in Kunark. They reworked them really well
Fav. TV Show: 7 Days
Fav. Author: Too many to list here
non-EQ hobbies: I actually manage to get in about 5 workouts a week.
Was a nationally ranked amateur wrestler in high
school and University, so I try too keep that going.
I design Web applications on the side of my job (don't
tell them that). I read voraciously. Hehe I also
like experimenting on my facial hair - Beard, Goatee,
Mutton Chops.....cause I can...that's why.
